ion\">&lt;</span>rt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>pīnyīn<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>rt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ruby</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>运行结果: <ruby>这是<rt>zhèshì</rt></ruby><ruby>拼音<rt>pīnyīn</rt></ruby></p>\n<h2 id=\"ruby-不兼容性的回退方案rp-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ruby-%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9E%E9%80%80%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88rp-\" aria-label=\"ruby 不兼容性的回退方案rp  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;ruby /&gt;</code>不兼容性的回退方案<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;rp /&gt;</code></h2>\n<p>因为web标准的兼容性，<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;rp /&gt;</code></a>被用来作为<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;ruby /&gt;</code>注音不支持的回退方案。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;rp /&gt;</code>的使用方法如下(需要围绕<code class=\"language-text\">rt</code>的开、闭标签):</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ruby</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n这是 <span c